showNowBtn.description: When showTime is displayed, select a button for the current time.
showNowBtn.description_zh: 是否显示 showTime 时，选择当前时间的按钮。

showTime.description: Whether to increase the time selection

:timepickerProps.description: For the parameters of time display, refer to TimePickerProps, which is the same as showTime.
:timepickerProps.description_zh: 时间显示的参数，参考 TimePickerProps，作用同 showTime。

:value.description: The value of the calendar component

:disabledTime.description: The time that cannot be selected

format.description: For the format of the display date, see dayjs. When you use string, you can manually type and edit the date. When using (value: Dayjs) => string, only dates can be selected in the picker.
format.description_zh: 展示日期的格式，参考dayjs。使用 string 时，可以手动键入和编辑日期。使用 (value: Dayjs) => string 时，只能在 Picker 中选取日期。
